                  <p><person role="3" project-ref="JAIFRP-00304">Paul Horowitz</person> - hat shop prop - 421 SW Stark St owns building in which <person role="1" wra-ref="502052">Hara</person> operates pool hall + bath house @ $10 per mo rental. Got bldg. in 1941. <person role="1" wra-ref="502052">Hara</person> has sold 4 bath tubs + 3 wash basins for $35.00 claims to not know name of purchaser. <person role="3" project-ref="JAIFRP-00304">Horowitz</person>advises he purchased 2 pool tables for $45 - paid $5.00 down. <person role="1" wra-ref="502052">Hara</person> interviewed today - says he purchased all contents for $40.00 about 6 yrs ago, including bath fixtures - says he has now sold pool tables to another party - is very profane, indifferent as to what may happen to him, is 60 years of age. <person role="1" wra-ref="502052">Hara</person> thought he might be able to call at our office in 1 week - not sooner.</p>
